Justin Roiland and Cartoon Network have parted ways but how will it affect the next 5 years of Rick and Morty? Ant Man 3 is sure to have some casualties...but who is gonna bite the bullet in what could be the final Ant Man installment? We do our best to speculate on ALL of these things and get into our topic of the week: Characters We Want To See In Live Action! Check it out!

